    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Prosobranchia having 7 denticles or teeth; most are herbivorous, but a few families are parasites or predators.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
